column5: 11 tags caught so far. Met an OFNer beside me with his son, his name is Tony, nice meeting you Tony, sorry I forgot your board name. May see you next weekend. Some pictures taken of our 2 days.  Tony                           This is what you win if your ticket entry is pulled    Picture of our group, 3 didn't get in the picture.
Man dat's a lot of boats and some aren't even in the water.  I think I'd avoid weekends there at all cost, insane I tell you, insane!
Believe me Chris, if a few of the guys that went were retired, we'd be there mid week. Week-ends are crazy  .

Hey Dave, it was great meeting you out on the water as well. My son Alexander(fishman2202) and I had a great time on Saturday. Non-stop action from the time we got there. It was funny seeing him catch those jumbos on a bare jigheads after we ran out of our minnows!!!  Thanks for the picture of us on our boat. That’s one of the best picture of the boat if seen. I'm stuck in the city this week-end so I won’t be out there again. Oh well, I guess I'll have to make time in the next few week-ends to get back out on the water.  Tony
